from green robert greenstein subject re accupuncture and aid in article euclid euclid k write aliceb alouse taylor write a friend of mine be see an acupuncturist and want to know if there be any danger of get aid from the needle ask the practitioner whether he use the pre-sterilized disposable needle or if he reuse needle sterilize them between use in the former case there no conceivable way to get aid from the needle in the latter case it highly unlikely though many practitioner use the disposable variety anyway it be illegal to perform acupuncture with unsterilized needle no license practitioner would dare do thi also there be not a single document case of transmission of aid vium acupuncture needle i would worry about it robert greenstein what the fool can not learn he laugh at think green that by hi laughter he show superiority instead of latent idiocy m corelli 